data.description: This charming single-family home features 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 well-appointed bathrooms. It offers golf course views and stunning sunsets, making it a serene oasis in the coveted neighborhood of Binks Forest of The Landings. The property is situated in an A+ rated elementary school district. Golf enthusiasts will appreciate its proximity to the prestigious Wellington National Golf Club and the Wanderers Club, providing endless opportunities for golfing enjoyment and country club amenities. Many upgrades to the property have been done since the owner acquired the property in 2017, including a new roof (2019), renovated kitchen and bathrooms, new driveway pavers, new A/C unit, and surveillance system. Don't miss this opportunity to reside in a comfortable home in Wellington.
